high_descs: Walk straight across the room to face the dresser.
Pick up the keys on the left side of the dresser.
Step back and face the top right drawer of the dresser.
Place the keys in the top shelf of the dresser.
Look up to face the keys on the right side of the dresser.
Pick up the keys on the right side of the dresser.
Step back and look down to face the top right drawer of the dresser.
Place the keys in the dresser with the other keys.
anns.task_desc: To put two key chains in the top right dresser drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then turn left and walk up to the large wooden dresser.
Pick up the leftmost set of keys off of the dresser.
Turn around and walk forward, the turn left and walk towards the wall, turn left again to face the large wooden dresser.
Open the upper right drawer of the dresser and put the set of keys inside in the front right corner.
Take a step forward over to the large wooden dresser.
Pick up the set of keys off of the wooden dresser.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn around to face the wooden dresser.
Open the upper right drawer of the dresser and put the keys inside to the left of the set of keys that are already in there.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys into a drawer.

high_descs: Head to the dresser across the room
Take the keys from the left side of the dresser
Turn around, take a few steps to the right, turn around
Open the top drawer of the dresser
Put the keys in the drawer, close the drawer
Take the keys from the dresser
Turn around two times
Open the top drawer of the dresser, Put the keys in the drawer, close the drawer
anns.task_desc: put both sets of keys in the top drawer of the dresser
